{"tid":1188032,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"尼馬案女主將召開記者會：他未使用安全措施","createTime":"2019-06-06T04:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T06:05:12.000Z","uid":173952,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f0fd2cdd8352bb80066180473d433804a8d0c380","tid":1188032,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T04:12:49.000Z","msg":"6月6日訊 據《每日體育報》消息，尼馬性侵事件女主Najila Trindade Mendes de Souza將在當地時間週四下午4：00在聖保羅的一個警察局作證，隨後召開新聞記者會，公佈她對此次事件的看法。<br />\n<br />\n  巴西媒體Estadao從事件女主Najila的身邊人瞭解到Najila指控尼馬的原因，身邊人說Najila在與尼馬的第一次約會時，在巴黎的酒店內受到了尼馬的暴力對待，並且被強姦。<br />\n<br />\n  該事件女主角表示，當她與尼馬在房間內親吻擁抱時，她要求尼馬使用避孕套，但尼馬並不喜歡這一提議，認為這妨礙了他的表現，並且這一提議引起了尼馬的憤怒。Najila說，那時候尼馬失去了控制，開始毆打她，Najila受傷的情況也在聖保羅的醫院中被記錄下來。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CrqpRuV5_GM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCrqpRuV5_GM&d=M59wMjr1KB2wSFKn0iQ%2Bgg%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=6bccd0d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CrqpRuV5_GM</a>"},{"pid":"e3f73258a21f1a7d0673ba4567397980d41b6ab6","tid":1188032,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T04:16:30.000Z","msg":"尼馬：我一直都身體力行推動環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b92c8cd85c8d7b2b8c12f1c5b1da0bb3dcbd5909","tid":1188032,"uid":7435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T04:18:57.000Z","msg":"強姦/被強姦都要插水lur地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d9c932bb2dc467acf3651ea0b40711e833310e","tid":1188032,"uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T04:20:56.000Z","msg":"關鍵條片同女主角口供係一致<br />\n有心造佢，之後條片應該條女會被姦"},{"pid":"97faff7c6a08a3ac96baeb2f09485631e6c78946","tid":1188032,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T04:32:33.000Z","msg":"條女係咪美斯請黎陰佢，影響佢打美洲盃?"},{"pid":"0de62eaea2b3d57ef6a1dc9da4c9a7ec5bfe8452","tid":1188032,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"